Manufacturer and distributor of irrigation equipment, accessories and supplies. Products include erosion control products, geotextiles and inlet protection. Types of geotextiles include non-woven, woven stabilization, monofilament, high-strength and spun-bonded fabrics. Inlet protection products such as grate bags, spring berms, bonding strips, filters and floating oil absorbent barriers are available. Meets ASTM and DOT standards. Made in the USA.

Company Description by Thomasnet
Manufacturer of fluid control & safety products & battery accessories. Fluid control products include grease guns, industrial buckets, recycling & draining systems, funnels, measuring containers, oil pans, oilers, pour spouts & scoops. Battery accessories include chargers, maintainers, disconnects, taps, fuse holders, monitors, isolators, ignition panels & circuit breakers. Maintenance & safety products include cable tie anchors, cleansers, radiator/heater hose repair kits, winter survival accessories, bumpers, mats, trays & third hand products. Suitable for home, workplace, road, campground & water applications.
Company Description by Wirthco Engineering, Inc.
WirthCo Engineering, Inc. is entering our third decade as a prime manufacturer of practical products for making life easier and safer - at home, in the workplace, on the road, in the campground, and on the water. We are grateful for valued employees and customers, and we are dedicated to continuing growth based upon integrity and service. We are also proud of our heritage of providing innovative quality products.

The innovative quality of WirthCos products is reflected in over 20 patents, a number that continues to grow. Our products have been proven, both in the laboratory and the marketplace. In addition to marketing our WirthCo brand, we proudly serve some of the worlds largest and most successful distributors and retailers which have selected WirthCo products for distribution under their own names. An exciting new element of WirthCo is the three trademarks we have recently developed: Battery Doctor, Funnel King, and Camp N E-Z.

Manufacturer of irrigation pump controllers. Available as automatic flow controls. Features include diaphragm assembly design construction with constant flow rating. Flow controls are available in pipe sizes from 1/4 in. to 1-1/2 in., flow ratings from 2/10 gpm to 100 gpm, overall lengths from 2 in. to 8-7/8 in., differential pressure ratings from 15 psid to 150 psid and operating temperatures from 32 degrees F to 160 degrees F with +/-10% accuracy. Flow controls can be used for large flow rating applications.
